For PIR Fixed vendor indicator Flag
With Plant and Material, 

Y => Fixed vendor and PIR exist
EORD-FLIFN [Indicator: Fixed Supplier] = X OR EORD.FEBEL [Fixed Outline Purchase Agreement Item] = X 
and 
record exists with same plant, vendor number and material in EINA and EINE tables

N => PIR exist and no Fixed Vendor SL
EORD-FLIFN <> X AND EORD.FEBEL <> X 
and
PIR record exists with same plant, vendor number and material in EINA and EINE tables

N => PIR NOT exist and no Fixed Vendor SL

EORD-FLIFN <> X AND EORD.FEBEL <> X 
and
PIR NO record exists with same plant, vendor number and material in EINA and EINE tables



Else “blank” (NOT APPLICABLE]


Message
If buy part [MARC-BESKZ = F or MARC-BESKZ = F  & 30 (MARC-SOBSL) – Special procurement type
] and PIR Fixed vendor indicator= “N” or “BLANK”, error –> Fixed Vendor

If PIR Fixed vendor indicator= Y, no message 

